-- England's Joe Cole Signs for Liverpool on Four-Year Contract, Club Says
-- Peter-Joseph Hegarty
-- 2010-07-19T13:10:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-19/england-s-joe-cole-signs-for-liverpool-on-four-year-contract-club-says.html

          
          
                  July 19 (Bloomberg) - Premier League soccer team Liverpool
signed England forward Joe Cole on a four-year deal, the club
said on its website. He was out of contract at his previous
team, Chelsea.  
          
          


  


        